org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model

Enum InputEnum

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<InputEnum>
      • org.lfenergy.operatorfabric.cards.model.InputEnum
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<InputEnum>

    public enum InputEnum
extends java.lang.Enum<InputEnum>
    The type of input
    TEXT
    This input will be displayed as an input text
    LIST
    This input will be displayed as a dropbox
    MULTI_LIST
    This input will be displayed as multivalued list input
    SWITCH_LIST
    This input is displayed as two list whose values may be exchanged
    LONG_TEXT
    This input will be displayed as a multi line input text
    BOOLEAN
    This input will be displayed as a boolean
    STATIC
    This input won't be displayed, it may serve as a constant parameter
    Note : This enum is created by hand because Swagger can't handle enums. It should match the corresponding enum definition in the Cards API.
